title: WholeBody 5.1 Demo
description:

transcripts: Hi I want to introduce you to the whole body 5.1 message chair this is a great introduction massage chair that can really help to soothe, tired, aching and sore muscles. If this chair has three 15-minute pre-programmed massages that each can target specific areas of your body for relief you've got the full back, upper back and lower back programs. This also has patent pending flex five technology. This technology would be like having massage and having a warm oil massage it is so smooth, you don't feel any friction like you could if you were having a dry massage from a masseuse that warm oil feel is a great asset for this chair. Another convenient feature of the whole body 5.1 massage chair is the swivel base this chair allows you to swivel up to 55 degrees for ease of positioning. The whole body 5.1 massage chair also has a foot and calf massager that has patented figure 8 technology. This technology unlike many others doesn't just clamp but in the ankle and foot, it actually goes around your calf and leg in an upward motion forcing blood back to the heart for improved circulation. If your legs can't take a massage at a certain point or maybe you just don't want to experience that feature right then it has a calf that can flip into an ottoman and you can just relax your legs on top in comfort.
